{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cc5215f701","title":"对随行部队的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7855628cdc","index":0,"year":1935,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"cc5215f701"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"895fea0469","type":"paragraph","text":"对随行部队的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"cc5215f701"},{"id":"a4b691636c","type":"paragraph","text":"1935年11月5日）从江西瑞金算起，我们走了一年多时间。我们每人开动两兵脚，走了二万五千里。这是从来未有过的长征。我们红军的人数比以前是少了一些，但是留下来的是革命的精华，都是经过严酸锻炼与考验的。留下来的同志不仅要以一当十，而且要以一当百、当千。今后，我们要和陕北红军、陕北人民团结一致，要做团结的模范，共同完成中国革命的伟大使命，开创中国革命新局面","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"cc5215f701"}],"page":{"id":"0e7005ac6a","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"cc5215f701","start":40,"end":40}}}},"__N_SSG":true}